## Module Architecture

- **AppModule** — global config, wires TypeORM + BullMQ roots, registers `JwtAuthGuard` as `APP_GUARD`; imports all 8 feature modules
- **AuthModule** — JWT guard/strategy/decorator only; no entity; exports `JwtAuthGuard`
- **UserModule** — User entity + JWT issuance; all routes are `@Public()`
- **ApifyModule** — `APIFY_CLIENT` injection token (factory from ConfigService), exports `ApifyLinkedinJobsService`
- **JobModule** — imports `ApifyModule`, registers all 8 job entities, exports `LocationRepository`, `ExperienceLevelRepository`, `JobDescriptionRepository`, `ApifyLinkedinJobsService`, all lookup repos
- **OllamaModule** — stateless, no imports; provides and exports `OllamaCvService` and `OllamaJobScoringService`
- **CandidateModule** — imports `OllamaModule` + `JobModule`; exports `CandidateProfileRepository`
- **CandidateApplicationModule** — imports `CandidateModule`; owns `candidate_application` + `application_status` tables
- **JobScoringModule** — imports `OllamaModule` + `JobModule` + `CandidateModule`; owns job-scoring BullMQ queue

## Key Patterns

- **Feature-based organization** under `src/module/<feature>/`
- **Global JWT guard** — `JwtAuthGuard` applied via `APP_GUARD`; use `@Public()` decorator to opt out
- **Constructor injection** everywhere; `@Inject('APIFY_CLIENT')` for factory token; `@InjectQueue` for BullMQ
- **Repository pattern** — abstract `BaseRepository<T>` with `findAll`, `create`, `insertManyIgnoreConflicts`
- **DTOs** for all validated inputs (request body + query params); use `class-validator` + `class-transformer`; `PaginationDto` base class for paginated queries
- **Barrel exports** — each subfolder has `index.ts` re-exporting its members; exceptions: `repository/` has no barrel; `dto/` may have barrel (`user/dto/index.ts`) or not
- **Interfaces** prefixed with `I` (e.g., `IJobDescription`, `ICompany`)
- **No Swagger/OpenAPI** decorators
- **Ollama config** read at module instantiation from `ollamaConfig` singleton (env-driven, no ConfigService injection)
- **CORS** enabled in `main.ts`; origin controlled by `DASHBOARD_URL` env var

## HTTP Endpoints

### Authentication (public — no JWT required)
| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/user/register` | Create account → returns `{ accessToken, refreshToken }` |
| POST | `/user/login` | Authenticate → returns `{ accessToken, refreshToken }` |
| POST | `/user/refresh` | Rotate refresh token → returns `{ accessToken }` |

### App
| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/` | Health check |

### Job Ingestion
| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/job-description` | Paginated + filtered job list (`ListJobFiltersDto`) |
| GET | `/job-description/:id` | Single job by id |
| POST | `/job-description/process-new-jobs` | Trigger LinkedIn scrape via Apify + ETL |
| POST | `/job-description/process-from-file` | Load jobs from local `jobsList.json` (dev/testing) |

### Lookup tables (each returns `{ items: [{id, name}] }`)
| Method | Path |
|---|---|
| GET | `/apply-type` |
| GET | `/company` |
| GET | `/contract-type` |
| GET | `/experience-level` |
| GET | `/location` |
| GET | `/sector` |
| GET | `/speciality` |

### Candidate Profile
| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/candidate-profile` | Paginated list |
| GET | `/candidate-profile/:id` | Single profile by id |
| POST | `/candidate-profile/process-cv` | Parse CV file via Ollama, upsert CandidateProfile |

### Candidate Applications
| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/candidate-profile/:candidateProfileId/applications` | List applications |
| POST | `/candidate-profile/:candidateProfileId/applications` | Create application |
| GET | `/candidate-profile/:candidateProfileId/applications/:applicationId` | Get application |
| PATCH | `/candidate-profile/:candidateProfileId/applications/:applicationId` | Update status / date |
| DELETE | `/candidate-profile/:candidateProfileId/applications/:applicationId` | Delete application (204) |

### Job Scoring
| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/job-scoring/candidate/:candidateId` | Paginated + filtered scores (`ListScoresRequestDto`) |
| POST | `/job-scoring/score-all` | Dispatch BullMQ scoring jobs for all unscored jobs |
| POST | `/job-scoring/clear-queue` | Clear pending scoring queue |

## Scripts

- `npm run start:dev` — dev with watch
- `npm run migration:generate -- src/module/<feature>/migrations/<name>` — auto-generate
- `npm run migration:run` — apply pending
- `npm run migration:revert` — rollback last
- `npm run lint` — ESLint with `--fix`
